beer.beer_description: In with the old and with the new! A Northern Hemisphere West Coast-style IPA showcasing Cascade, the hop variety that helped launch the craft beer revolution and Idaho #7, a relative new varietal on the scene that is turning heads. Displaying strong notes of pine, citrus and floral with a lingering bitterness.
